Nord + Vampire Lord,
Skills: Conjuration, Destruction, Illusion, Alteration, Light Armour,
descriptionHtml:
Hi threre, I made this character just for fun actually. It`s a vampire lord with a few quest`s done and I hacked some of the perks.
